    "causal_summary": "`sk-code` and `sk-doc` (the other two parent hubs in this repo) both carry two structural conventions in their `mode-registry.json`/`hub-router.json` that `sk-design`'s equivalents lack: (1) a per-mode `\"command\"` field recording the bound slash command, documented in `advisorRoutingContract`; (2) a `\"hub-identity\"` vocabulary class wired into every mode's `routerSignals.classes` array",
